#HELPS
91 EXTRA BITS~
`@i`$TEM EXTRA B`@i`$TS`@:``
   1 - Glowing            2048 - Anti_neutral
   2 - Humming            4096 - Noremove
   4 - Dark               8192 - Inventory
  16 - Evil              16384 - Nopurge
  32 - Invis             32768 - Rot_death 
  64 - Magic             65536 - Vis_death 
 128 - No_drop          524288 - No_locate 
 256 - Bless           3355432 - No_uncurse 
 512 - Anti_good       4194304 - Sell_extract 
1024 - Anti_evil      16777216 - Burn_proof
 
SYNTAX:
set object <obj name> extra <bit #>
 
Note:
To have more than one extra bit, add the numbers.
(Ie, 1 + 2 = 3 = (Glowing) (Humming) )
~

92 LIQUIDS~
`^L`6IQUID `^T`6YPES``
 0 - Water            18 - White Wine
 1 - Beer             19 - Champagne
 2 - Red Wine         20 - Mead
 3 - Ale              21 - Rose Wine
 4 - Dark Ale         22 - Benedictine Wine
 5 - Whisky           23 - Vodka
 6 - Lemonaide        24 - Cranberry Juice
