10 - Milk             28 - Aquavit
11 - Tea              29 - Schnapps
12 - Coffee           30 - Icewine
13 - Blood            31 - Amontillado
14 - Salt Water       32 - Sherry
15 - Coke             33 - Framboise
16 - Root Beer        34 - Rum
17 - Elvish Wine      35 - Cordial

SYNTAX:
