~

92 WEAPON AFFECTS V4~
`$WEAPON`@-`$AFFECTS`@:``
0 - Nothing                  16 - Vorpal
1 - Flaming                  32 - Two-Handed
2 - Frost                    64 - Shocking
4 - Vampiric                128 - Poison
8 - Sharp
 
SYNTAX:
set object <obj name> v4 <weap aff #>
 
Note:
To add the affects, simply add the numbers.
(Ie, 1 + 2 = 3 = Flaming & Vampiric Weapon.)
~

